snippet.textDisplay: Hey Tati! I absolutely love you, your videos, your kind heartedness, and the time and efforts you put into every one of your products. I purchased and  received the Tati Beauty pallet back in the middle of December. I was curious to see if the pans are supposed to be glued into the pallet or are they only supposed to be magneticly attached? Because about 2 weeks after using the pallet everyday it accidentally slid off the couch about maybe 1 -1.5 feet off the ground. When it hit the ground every pan fell out, so I had to go to the website to see which order they were supposed to be in.. and while picking them all up off the floor they all survived except Memory Matt unfortunately. So I just wanted to let you know that they fall out of the pallet very easily..  I still absolutely love this pallet and use it everyday! I'll probably end up buying another. Thanks for being such a great person Tati. I hope you and your family have a wonderful year!!
